<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>很遗憾，您访问的页面出错了</title>
    <style>
        * {
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        html,
        body {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            position: relative;
            background: #F6F7F9;
            font-family: "Microsoft YaHei";
        }

        #error404_main {
            height: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        #error404_main .error-box {
            width: 450px;
            height: 279px;
            background: url(/images/404.png) no-repeat top center;
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            margin-left: -225px;
            top: 50%;
            margin-top: -139.5px;
        }

        #error404_main .error-box .errtxt {
            width: 100%;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 64px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666666;
        }

        .back_btn {
            background: url(/images/back_btn.png) no-repeat center center;
            width: 92px;
            height: 34px;
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            margin-left: -46px;
            bottom: 0;
            font-size: 0;
            text-indent: -9999px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="error404_main" class="main-content">
        <div class="error-box">
            <div class="errtxt">很遗憾，您访问的页面出错了...</div>
            <a href="/" class="back_btn">返回首页</a>
        </div>
    </div>
